#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid "A simple ball dodging game."
msgstr "Preprosta igra izogibanja žogi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to play"
msgstr "Kako igrati"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "Objective:"
msgstr "Cilj:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "Let the blue ball move in the field without touching the red balls."
msgstr "Naj se modra žoga premika po polju, ne da bi se dotaknila rdečih žog."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kollision; Game Board"
msgstr "&kollision; Igralna plošča"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the empty field to start a game: a blue ball immediately replaces "
"your mouse cursor, and a number of red balls start to fade into the field."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na prazno polje, da začnete igro: modra krogla takoj nadomesti "
"kazalec miške in številne rdeče kroglice začnejo bledeti v polju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the red balls finish materializing, they move at a random speed in a "
"random direction, and you have to promptly dodge them moving the blue ball "
"inside the field with your mouse. After some time, other red balls will "
"appear, fading in as before and then starting to move. Be prepared to avoid "
"them, too."
msgstr ""
"Ko se rdeče kroglice končajo z materializacijo, se premikajo z naključno "
"hitrostjo v naključno smer, vi pa se jim morate nemudoma izogniti, tako da z "
"miško premikate modro kroglico znotraj polja. Čez nekaj časa se bodo "
"pojavile druge rdeče kroglice, ki bodo zbledele kot prej in se nato začele "
"premikati. Bodite pripravljeni, da se jim tudi izognete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can choose the game difficulty level on the right of the status bar. The "
"higher the difficulty level, the faster red balls move, and the more balls "
"will appear on the play field."
msgstr ""
"Na desni strani vrstice stanja lahko izberete težavnostno stopnjo igre. "
"Višja kot je težavnostna stopnja, hitreje se premikajo rdeče kroglice in več "
"žog se bo pojavilo na igrišču."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Game Rules, Strategies and Tips</title>"
msgstr "<title>Pravila, strategije in nasveti igre</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Game Rules, Strategies and Tips</para>"
msgstr "<para>Pravila igre, strategije in nasveti</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules"
msgstr "Pravila igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Red balls move with constant speed on the game field bouncing off walls "
"until colliding with another ball, which causes the speed and direction of "
"both balls to change."
msgstr ""
"Rdeče žoge se premikajo s konstantno hitrostjo po igralnem polju in se "
"odbijajo od sten, dokler ne trčijo z drugo žogico, kar povzroči spremembo "
"hitrosti in smeri obeh žog."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "The blue ball can be freely moved inside the field with the mouse."
msgstr "Modro kroglo lahko z miško prosto premikate po polju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The blue ball cannot escape the field. If the cursor is moved out, the ball "
"stays on the edge, until the cursor returns."
msgstr ""
"Modra žoga ne more pobegniti iz polja. Če se kazalec premakne ven, žogica "
"ostane na robu, dokler se kazalec ne vrne."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "The score is directly proportional to the time the game has lasted."
msgstr "Rezultat je neposredno sorazmeren s časom trajanja igre."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pausing the game subtracts a (cumulative) 5 seconds penalty from the total "
"time."
msgstr ""
"Če prekinete igro, se od skupnega časa odšteje (kumulativno) 5 sekund kazni."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Strategije in nasveti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Move the blue ball gently and slowly. Swinging across the field will make "
"collisions with other balls more likely."
msgstr ""
"Nežno in počasi premikajte modro kroglo. Z nihanjem čez polje bodo trki z "
"drugimi žogicami bolj verjetni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Moving the cursor out of the field can be used as an elegant trick to come "
"out of a screwed situation. Use it wisely."
msgstr ""
"Premikanje kazalca izven polja lahko uporabite kot eleganten trik za izhod "
"iz brezupne situacije. Uporabljajte ga pametno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do not pause the game unless absolutely necessary."
msgstr "Ne prekinjajte igre, razen če je to nujno potrebno."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "Interface Overview"
msgstr "Pregled vmesnika"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu Items"
msgstr "Elementi menija"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>End game</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Končaj igro</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "End a game and return to the welcome screen."
msgstr "Končajte igro in se vrnite na pozdravni zaslon."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>P</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Pause</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>P</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Premor</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pauses or resumes the game."
msgstr "Začasno ustavi ali nadaljuje igro."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show High Scores</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prikaži najboljše rezultate</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "This will show the best scores for the current level."
msgstr "To bo pokazalo najboljše rezultate za trenutno raven."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapusti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting this item will end your current game, and exit &kollision;."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete ta element, boste končali trenutno igro in zapustili &kollision;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Play Sounds</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Predvajaj zvoke</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Toggle whether sound effects should be played.</action> The default "
"is off."
msgstr ""
"<action>Preklopite, ali naj se predvajajo zvočni učinki.</action> Privzeto "
"je izklopljeno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Increase Ball Size</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Povečaj velikost žoge</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Toggle to make the balls bigger.</action> The default is off."
msgstr ""
"<action>Preklopite, da povečate kroglice.</action> Privzeto je izklopljeno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Difficulty</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Težavnost</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows you to select a difficulty <guilabel>Easy</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Medium</guilabel>, <guilabel>Hard</guilabel> for the game."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča vam izbiro težavnosti igre <guilabel>Enostavno</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Srednje</guilabel>, <guilabel>Težko</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &kollision; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"and <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the "
"sections about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega &kollision; ima skupno &kde; Elemente menija <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> in <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu>, za več informacij preberite razdelke o "
"<ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">meniju z "
"nastavitvami</ulink> in <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help"
"\">meni Pomoč</ulink> v &kde; Osnove."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "Pogosto zastavljena vprašanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid "I want to change the way this game looks. Can I?"
msgstr "Želim spremeniti videz te igre. Ali lahko?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>No.</para>"
msgstr "<para>Ne.</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play the game?"
msgstr "Ali lahko uporabljam tipkovnico za igranje igre?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. &kollision; can only be played with a mouse."
msgstr "Ne. &kollision; se lahko igra samo z miško."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid "I cannot figure out what to do here! Are there hints?"
msgstr "Ne morem ugotoviti, kaj naj naredim tukaj! Ali obstajajo namigi?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kollision; does not have a <quote>Hint</quote> feature."
msgstr "&kollision; nima funkcije <quote>Namig</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I have to quit the game now, but I am not finished yet. Can I save my "
"progress?"
msgstr ""
"Zdaj moram zapustiti igro, vendar še nisem končal. Ali lahko shranim svoj "
"napredek?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid "You cannot save games in &kollision;."
msgstr "Iger ne morete shraniti v &kollision;."

